  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"uee759aec\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀的文档编辑器支持块级操作。</span></p><h1 id=\"PIY7j\"><span class=\"ne-text\">块的定义</span></h1><p id=\"u48347896\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">块的最小粒度，是能单独成行的内容。如一个段落，一个卡片。有些布局卡片中，可以嵌套其他的块。</span></p><h1 id=\"h0sAe\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如何使用</span></h1><p id=\"ub581035f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">将鼠标悬浮在块的附近，即可看到一个块的锚点</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663834236554-8494570b-87f6-4957-9340-9980a0bd5144.png\" width=\"20\" id=\"u4e8c4d68\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">。点击可以打开查看对这个块的操作内容。拖拽可以调整块的位置。</span></p><p id=\"u517de0d4\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663834344017-8559455c-8f0d-4014-abdd-178fba91b556.png\" width=\"844\" id=\"uecd82d68\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h1 id=\"dGg7f\"><span class=\"ne-text\">块拖拽</span></h1><p id=\"ufe12b693\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">拖拽</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663834236554-8494570b-87f6-4957-9340-9980a0bd5144.png\" width=\"20\" id=\"nEedC\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可以调整块的位置。在对应的位置出现蓝色的位置示意。</span></p><h2 id=\"kRaLp\"><span class=\"ne-text\">拖拽实现排序</span></h2><p id=\"u040fc522\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/gif/268442/1663839162231-0fd7cad4-65b9-4e9b-8406-b476dcec7fe8.gif\" width=\"1042\" id=\"u11aeeb20\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h2 id=\"DFNrP\"><span class=\"ne-text\">拖拽实现缩进</span></h2><p id=\"ueae03a25\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">将块拖拽进列表，即可创建缩进关系。可以通过拖拽，将块插入到列表前一个项的同级和子级。</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/gif/268442/1663844570780-a2d9bf56-497b-482c-b164-fd360e37124a.gif\" width=\"838\" id=\"u150e338a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h2 id=\"epNK6\"><span class=\"ne-text\">拖拽实现嵌套</span></h2><p id=\"ud726fc1a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可以拖拽块进入其他布局块。比如高亮块、引用块、分栏块、折叠块。</span></p><p id=\"uc6a955ad\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">比如，将文本拖进高亮块。</span></p><p id=\"ud29d911d\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/gif/268442/1663844795162-6c9f4f18-dec4-44d6-910e-2f1651d9903b.gif\" width=\"800\" id=\"u6cd67546\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u182c8434\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">再比如，将文本拖进分栏卡片。</span></p><p id=\"u360ce0d8\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/gif/268442/1663845004159-1421670d-cd2d-43b2-b0ce-7b4dc27f4dc8.gif\" width=\"800\" id=\"u66dff554\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h1 id=\"SZLu8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">块转化</span></h1><p id=\"udcace52d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在锚点中</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663834236554-8494570b-87f6-4957-9340-9980a0bd5144.png\" width=\"20\" id=\"znPm0\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击块转化，可看到面板选项。</span></p><p id=\"u6ddfd6ba\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663835768896-9d496502-3df8-45b3-bf50-69865f62e046.png\" width=\"178\" id=\"u4cdbaafb\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u9d8231c3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击上方的选项，可转化文本格式。支持的文本格式有 正文、各级标题（1-4）、列表（无序列表、有序列表、任务列表）、代码块等。点击即可切换到对应的格式。如正文转化为列表，列表转化为正文等。</span></p><p id=\"u06bc4192\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击下方的布局类卡片，如高亮块、引用块，可快速在当前块外侧添加块容器。再次点击，即可去除容器。</span></p><p id=\"u9bf58f29\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663835878936-ae0d690f-6d7e-449a-9465-c5528d8ceca0.png\" width=\"144\" id=\"ub6824789\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h1 id=\"cWv9A\"><span class=\"ne-text\">块缩进</span></h1><p id=\"uee8efe08\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在锚点</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663834236554-8494570b-87f6-4957-9340-9980a0bd5144.png\" width=\"20\" id=\"ybN27\" class=\"ne-image\"><span class=\"ne-text\">中点击缩进，可增加和减少缩进。</span></p><p id=\"uf691f8e4\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663840601630-2376c531-5389-41e4-8b92-df1cb212e80a.png\" width=\"992\" id=\"ua63b15d8\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u2862d00c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">可对所有的块设置缩进。包括表格、画板、代码块、折叠块等。分栏卡片目前还不支持缩进，敬请期待。</span></p><p id=\"uf6a8d971\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">对文本块，也支持光标在行首按下</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">tab</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">快捷设置缩进。</span></p><h1 id=\"zNP48\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在下方添加</span></h1><p id=\"u18fc83df\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击任何块的锚点，都可在该块的下方添加内容。</span></p><p id=\"u836e7398\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1663837303791-ae29f199-616d-40c3-8976-a289ae14f0e0.png\" width=\"970\" id=\"uc5a1c1e7\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uc9a7b594\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h1 id=\"E5j9D\"><span class=\"ne-text\">推荐用法</span></h1><h2 id=\"mWyi1\"><span class=\"ne-text\">给文本添加高亮</span></h2><p id=\"u92d806c0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击下方的布局类卡片，如高亮块、引用块，可快速在当前块外侧添加块容器。再次点击，即可去除容器。</span></p><p id=\"u70112b24\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/gif/268442/1663836186155-7f184ecf-cd55-4ced-9e45-11b8f78c6850.gif\" width=\"1042\" id=\"ubc2c5895\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u5a157667\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><h2 id=\"QKPVg\"><span class=\"ne-text\">将文本拖入分栏卡片</span></h2><p id=\"ucdbdb824\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/gif/268442/1663845031819-1022ab72-48d0-44a5-b1c1-9d1c304c611b.gif\" width=\"800\" id=\"NqhpF\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><h1 id=\"jEpDT\"><span class=\"ne-text\">拖拽列表排序</span></h1><p id=\"ufba1c119\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">拖拽列表会带动子项一起排序。<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/gif/268442/1663845153490-4f865c66-614b-4eea-b15b-7b900fd0e0f1.gif\" width=\"850\" id=\"ue7e20ce3\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u9b861bb1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道 </span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">  感谢你的支持！</span></p></div>",
